}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:11;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"slide in\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:12;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"welcome mat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=129259\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:622:\"<p>Are you looking for ways to increase registrations for your course, offline classes, or online school? In this case study, we share how Singularity University generated 967 new leads for their university using a single optin, and so much more. This case study is packed full with examples and experiments you can use to see [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-singularity-university-967-new-leads-one-optin/\">How Singularity University Generated 967 New Leads From One Optin</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Angie Meeker\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12210:\"<p>Are you looking for ways to <strong>increase registrations for your course</strong>, offline classes, or online school? In this case study, we share how Singularity University generated 967 new leads for their university using a single optin, and so much more. This case study is <em><strong>packed full</strong></em> with examples and experiments you can use to see similar results today.</p>\n<h3>Meet Singularity University</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://su.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Singularity University</a> helps transform leaders, organizations, and entire industries to help them thrive and ultimately create positive change.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129260\" style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity-Uses-OptinMonster.png\" alt=\"Singularity Uses OptinMonster\" width=\"800\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity-Uses-OptinMonster.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity-Uses-OptinMonster-300x185.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity-Uses-OptinMonster-768x472.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>Singularity uses OptinMonster in a variety of ways, from their highest-traffic articles to niche landing pages and event registration. OptinMonster helps them maximize their content’s lead capture capabilities.</p>\n<h3>How Singularity Increases Event Registrations</h3>\n<p>When Singularity was preparing to launch their flagship event, <a href=\"https://su.org/summits/su-global-summit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Singularity University Global Summit</a>, they knew they needed a way to engage their community members who would not be able to attend in person.</p>\n<p>A live stream was the perfect solution! But, how could they remind folks to actually tune in?</p>\n<p>This <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/fullscreen-welcome-gate/\">fullscreen welcome mat</a> notified users when the livestream was going to happen and was incredibly successful! Singularity captured over 2,000 new email signups in less than nine days with this optin.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129261\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SIngularity_FullScreen.png\" alt=\"Singularity University uses an OptinMonster fullscreen to capture leads.\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SIngularity_FullScreen.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SIngularity_FullScreen-300x176.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SIngularity_FullScreen-768x450.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>The fullscreen welcome mat campaign <strong>converted 77% of visitors</strong>.</p>\n<p>As part of their promotion strategy for the MENA Global Impact Challenge, they ran a highly <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/geo-location-targeting/\">geo-location targeted optin</a> to 22 countries in the Middle East and North Africa. The goal of this highly targeted campaign was to get users located in a specific area to submit their application.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-129263 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_Mena.png\" alt=\"Singularity used geotargeting to show this campaign only to visitors from the Middle East and North Africa\" width=\"800\" height=\"543\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_Mena.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_Mena-300x204.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_Mena-768x521.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>This campaign <strong>converted 25% of visitors</strong> &#8211; one out of every four visitors! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f64c.png\" alt=\"🙌\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">Libratone also used geo-location targeting to make sure their campaigns matched the language of their visitors&#8217; location &#8211; and <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-libratone-grew-list-400-percent-with-geotargeting/\"><strong>grew their email list 400%</strong></a> as a result!</div>\n<h3>How Singularity Increased Newsletter Subscriptions</h3>\n<p>Next, Singularity set up this campaign on their four highest-traffic pages on their news media site, <a href=\"https://singularityhub.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://singularityhub.com/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1548955011996000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGYRH3Fmeffnu6o_Lr1BYKYfECCFw\">Singularity Hub</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129264\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity_Exit.png\" alt=\"Singularity University captures abandoning visitors with an exit-intent campaign.\" width=\"800\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity_Exit.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity_Exit-300x185.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Singularity_Exit-768x474.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>The campaign only appeared to visitors about to exit the site. It was triggered using our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\">exit-intent technology</a>. Exit-intent campaigns are triggered when a visitor’s mouse motions towards the browser bar, a sure sign they’re about to leave.</p>\n<p>Over a period of nine months, <strong>this exit-intent optin captured 967 new email addresses</strong> on just these four pages!</p>\n<p>Want to see it live in action? Check out one of these articles:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://singularityhub.com/2016/07/18/why-the-cost-of-living-is-poised-to-plummet-in-the-next-20-years/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://singularityhub.com/2016/07/18/why-the-cost-of-living-is-poised-to-plummet-in-the-next-20-years/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1548955011996000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEixTTVJ_WH6d3PHxor4qJvRM-L2A\">Why the Cost of Living Is Poised to Plummet in the Next 20 Years</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://singularityhub.com/2015/01/26/ray-kurzweils-mind-boggling-predictions-for-the-next-25-years/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://singularityhub.com/2015/01/26/ray-kurzweils-mind-boggling-predictions-for-the-next-25-years/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1548955011996000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFuEF9VpCSWvw8k7yzTxBGknxFHKw\">Ray Kurzweil’s Mind-Boggling Predictions for the Next 25 Years</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://singularityhub.com/2015/05/11/the-world-in-2025-8-predictions-for-the-next-10-years/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://singularityhub.com/2015/05/11/the-world-in-2025-8-predictions-for-the-next-10-years/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1548955011996000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFSP-Le5QFAftrJ6BIYqRbMnGyVRg\">The World in 2025: 8 Predictions for the Next 10 Years</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How Singularity Increased Leads With A Demo</h3>\n<p>Anyone who sells information products is familiar with this challenge: some users don’t want to immediately pay for a product. They want to see a portion of it first or try it out, to see if it’s a good fit for them.</p>\n<p>A simple <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/slide-in-forms/\">slide-in optin</a> on Singularity’s online course page promises to share a sneak peek of a course in exchange for an email address.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129267\" style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU-Slidein_demo.png\" alt=\"Singularity University drives course registration with a slide-in campaign.\" width=\"800\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU-Slidein_demo.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU-Slidein_demo-300x161.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU-Slidein_demo-768x413.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>These email addresses are then dropped into a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/mid-funnel-marketing-tactics/\">nurture campaign</a>, which helps them deliver additional value and track users through the funnel.</p>\n<p>This slide in campaign <strong>converted 10% of visitors</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Increasing Pageviews Using Button Redirects</h3>\n<p>One of Singularity&#8217;s earliest campaigns was pretty simple but very powerful. It wasn&#8217;t even designed to capture an email. Instead, they encouraged readers who were close to finishing one article to read another when they were done.</p>\n<p>Using a scroll trigger, the campaign below appeared when the visitor had read 80% of an article. It offered to send the reader to another article they would likely be interested in.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-129268\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_lightbox.png\" alt=\"Singularity University increases pageviews using OptinMonster.\" width=\"622\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_lightbox.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_lightbox-300x241.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/SU_lightbox-768x617.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 622px) 100vw, 622px\" /></p>\n<p>This simple prompt led <strong>20% of readers</strong> of the article to continue reading the next article in the series. This is a great method for increasing pageviews and average time on site.</p>\n<h3>Advice from Singularity on Tracking Leads with OptinMonster</h3>\n<p>When asked if they had any tips for OptinMonster users, Singularity responded with this valuable advice:</p>\n<blockquote><p>We have a very diverse lead capture program built out, and follow a strict campaign naming convention so that it’s easier to follow along in <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-view-optinmonster-reports-on-google-analytics/\">Google Analytics’ (GA) Events</a> section.</p>\n<p>Our naming convention for the title of each optin is “Optin Type &#8211; Initiative.” Since these optin titles populate as the Event title in GA, we find it easiest to sort campaigns by optin type and simply compare performance. While the names might seem complicated at first glance, keeping the naming convention consistent makes sorting inside GA much easier.</p>\n<p>GA Tip: When using the above naming convention and search for “optin” in GA Events, you can easily filter by optin type, campaign, date range, etc.</p>\n<p>We also use UTMs to track which optins are increasing conversions. It’s easy to measure this using GA, so we know if our Slide-In optin version A or our Mobile optin version B is getting more users to submit an application. Once we know which is more effective, we adjust our practices.</p></blockquote>\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<p>Singularity experimented with well-designed, well-placed campaigns and saw great results.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Singularity University <strong>registered 25% of location-targeted visitors</strong> for an event.</li>\n<li>Singularity University <strong>generated 967 new leads</strong> from a single optin.</li>\n<li>Singularity University <strong>kept 20% of visitors onsite</strong> longer using a redirect button.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Summary</h3>\n<p>Singularity University’s success using OptinMonster is the result of a thoughtful understanding of their readers’ needs. They took the time to consider the behaviors of their visitors, and exactly what they needed that individual visitor to do next, then used a variety of OptinMonster features to encourage them to do that.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-singularity-university-967-new-leads-one-optin/\">How Singularity University Generated 967 New Leads From One Optin</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-singularity-university-967-new-leads-one-optin/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"10 Ways To Get More Phone Calls From Your Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://optinmonster.com/get-more-phone-calls-from-your-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://optinmonster.com/get-more-phone-calls-from-your-website/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 22 Jan 2019 17:38:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"A/B testing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"click-to-call\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"exit intent\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"lead magnets\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"popups\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=128470\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:626:\"<p>People use their smartphones for everything these days. Including, to the surprise of some, actually making phone calls to businesses. Is your website ready to use phone calls to turn visitors into customers? Some businesses focus so much on their digital campaigns, they forget to integrate phone calls into their overall strategy. In this article, we&#8217;ll [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/get-more-phone-calls-from-your-website/\">10 Ways To Get More Phone Calls From Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12619:\"<p>People use their smartphones for everything these days. Including, to the surprise of some, <strong>actually making phone calls to businesses</strong>. Is your website ready to use phone calls to turn visitors into customers? Some businesses focus so much on their digital campaigns, they forget to integrate phone calls into their overall strategy.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you 10 ways to get more phone calls from your website. Let&#8217;s get started!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129309\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-stats.png\" alt=\"click to call is estimated to generate 13.7 billion in global revenue by 2020\" width=\"620\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-stats.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-stats-300x242.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>1. Put Your Number at the Top of Every Page</h3>\n<p>This first tip may seem obvious, but it&#8217;s surprising how many businesses forget to include their phone numbers on their website. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f631.png\" alt=\"😱\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>Make it easy for your visitors to find your phone number by including it at the top of every page. Be sure to include a click-to-call link, so visitors can call you without having to search for your number.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-129343\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/calllink.png\" alt=\"add a &quot;call us&quot; link to the top of your site\" width=\"619\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/calllink.png 550w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/calllink-300x130.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px\" /></p>\n<p>If you use WordPress for your site, head over to WPBeginner for an excellent step-by-step guide to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-add-clickable-phone-numbers-for-smartphones-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">adding a click-to-call button or link</a>. You can also take advantage of OptinMonster&#8217;s awesome <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-use-monsterlinks-to-load-your-popup-with-click-of-a-button/\">MonsterLinks™</a> feature to add a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-create-a-click-to-call-button/\">click-to-call popup</a>! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f60e.png\" alt=\"😎\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<h3>2. Put Your Number at the Bottom of Every Page</h3>\n<p>A recent <a href=\"http://www.invoca.com\">survey</a> shows that 68% of people will only search for a company&#8217;s phone number for about 2 minutes. After that, they&#8217;re moving on to your competitor.</p>\n<p>To make it easy for your potential customers, include your phone number at the bottom of each page too. An easy way to get this done without missing a page is to add it to your footer:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129340\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/fogro-footer.png\" alt=\"add your phone number to your site\'s footer\" width=\"620\" height=\"253\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/fogro-footer.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/fogro-footer-300x122.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>3. Optimize for Calls By Using A/B Testing</h3>\n<p>There are so many ways you can test your website to see what works and what doesn&#8217;t.</p>\n<p>Using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/8-ab-tests-to-run-on-your-popups-to-get-more-email-subscribers/\">A/B testing</a>, you can try things like placing your phone number on different parts of your webpage. Did the page with the phone number on the bottom right get more conversions? Or was it the page with the phone number on the bottom left?</p>\n<p>Other things you can test are the copy, color, and design.</p>\n<p>Test regularly so you can find the best ways to drive calls from your website.</p>\n<h3>4. Optimize Your Site for <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-increase-your-mobile-conversion-rate/\">Mobile</a></h3>\n<p>By 2020, the number of mobile phone users is expected to jump to <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/274774/forecast-of-mobile-phone-users-worldwide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">4.78 billion</a> worldwide.</p>\n<p>With so many people using mobile, you&#8217;ll want to make sure your website is properly optimized.</p>\n<p>To do this, make sure that the phone number on the website is clickable so that if a potential customer visits your website on their phone, they can tap the number to make a call.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s an example from Admind Creative Agency:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128487 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/mobilecall620.jpg\" alt=\"optimize for mobile\" width=\"620\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/mobilecall620.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/mobilecall620-300x242.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Using their phones, visitors are automatically taken to the call screen once they click on Admind&#8217;s phone number.</p>\n<h3>5. Include Your Number on Your Lead Magnets</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;re using <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com/9-lead-magnets-to-increase-subscribers/\">lead magnets</a> on your website, that&#8217;s another great opportunity for you to include your phone number.</p>\n<p>With these downloadable offers, people already want the content, so it&#8217;s likely they&#8217;ll be reading it.</p>\n<p>Provide your phone number within the pages in your lead magnet so potential customers will have it on-hand.</p>\n<h3>6. Use Your Number in Your Exit-Intent Popup</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/40-exit-popup-hacks-that-will-grow-your-subscribers-and-revenue/\">Exit-intent popups</a> are a great way to capture your visitor&#8217;s attention one last time before they leave your site.</p>\n<p>Add your phone number to the popup and get one more opportunity to generate a sale. Even better, add a click-to-call button so visitors know that you&#8217;re available to answer their questions.</p>\n<p>You can even use display rules to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-schedule-your-marketing-campaigns-with-optinmonster/\">show a popup with a click-to-call button during specific hours</a> when you know you&#8217;ll be available for phone calls&#8230;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129346\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-available.png\" alt=\"use display rules to show a click-to-call popup when you\'re available\" width=\"620\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-available.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-available-300x237.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Then, show a different popup that allows visitors to leave a message when you aren&#8217;t available!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129349\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-not-available.png\" alt=\"use display rules to show a wpform to leave a message when you\'re not available\" width=\"361\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-not-available.png 361w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/click-to-call-not-available-217x300.png 217w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 361px) 100vw, 361px\" /></p>\n<p>For inspiration, check out our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/exit-intent-popup-examples/\">exit-intent popup gallery</a>.</p>\n<h3>7. Don&#8217;t Forget to Include a Number for Every Location</h3>\n<p>If your business has more than one location, avoid listing a generic phone number that goes to an automated voicemail.</p>\n<p>Instead, list a specific phone number for each location. Check out this example below.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128489 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/heart620final.jpg\" alt=\"calls from your website\" width=\"620\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/heart620final.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/heart620final-300x242.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Heart, a coffee roaster in Portland, OR, shows info for both of their locations on their website, including the phone number for each.</p>\n<h3>8. Retarget Past Callers With Targeted Popups</h3>\n<p>Did you know that more than 70% of visitors get frustrated when content isn&#8217;t specific to their needs? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f62b.png\" alt=\"😫\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>If someone has a history of calling you, consider <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-personalize-popups-with-names/\">personalizing your popup</a>. A great way to do this is to use their names.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-126701\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"297\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize.png 297w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-176x300.png 176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" /></p>\n<p>Personalized popups are a great way to capture your visitors&#8217; attention because you can make them feel welcome. Use this as part of your strategy to get calls from your website.</p>\n<h3>9. Encourage Calls With Your Copy</h3>\n<p>Your website should encourage visitors to pick up the phone and call by using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/university/guides/700-power-words-that-will-boost-your-conversions/\">power words</a> to trigger emotions like trust and curiosity&#8230; Sometimes even fear. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f47b.png\" alt=\"👻\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>Heard of <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/fomo-marketing-examples-to-boost-sales/\">FOMO</a> (fear of missing out)? Fear is one of the most powerful motivators of all. Try using this strategy to inspire your visitors to take action and call you today.</p>\n<p>Power words such as &#8220;don&#8217;t miss out&#8221; are so persuasive that people simply can&#8217;t resist being influenced by them.</p>\n<p>Check out this example below:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128490 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pikesleaking.jpg\" alt=\"power words on popup\" width=\"313\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pikesleaking.jpg 313w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pikesleaking-211x300.jpg 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" /></p>\n<p>There&#8217;s even a click to call button at the bottom. Cool, right? <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f60e.png\" alt=\"😎\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<h3>10. Use Call Tracking &amp; Analytics</h3>\n<p>Tools like <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/google-analytics-101-how-to-track-your-conversions-step-by-step/\">Google Analytics</a> provide valuable insight into understanding how your customers interact with your website. You can combine it with call tracking software like <a href=\"https://www.invoca.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Invoca</a> or <a href=\"https://www.dialogtech.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">DialogTech</a> to bridge the gap between digital and inbound calls.</p>\n<p>By understanding your customers, you can start to deliver <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ultimate-ecommerce-personalization-guide/\">personalized customer experience</a>.</p>\n<p>And there you have it! From including a click-to-call button to personalizing popups, you&#8217;ve just learned 10 ways to get more calls to your business. For more actionable tips, check us out on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Optinmonster?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YouTube</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/get-more-phone-calls-from-your-website/\">10 Ways To Get More Phone Calls From Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://optinmonster.com/get-more-phone-calls-from-your-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"OptinMonster 2018 Recap: A Time of Monster Growth\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://optinmonster.com/optinmonster-2018-recap-a-time-of-monster-growth/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://optinmonster.com/optinmonster-2018-recap-a-time-of-monster-growth/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 18 Jan 2019 18:28:41 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"recap\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"year in review\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=129247\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:613:\"<p>It&#8217;s hard to believe that another year has already gone by. Cue Boyz II Men&#8217;s &#8220;It&#8217;s So Hard to Say Goodbye to Yesterday.&#8221; 2018 was an awesome year for OptinMonster. Our customers are the reason we exist, so it&#8217;s an amazing feeling to deliver a product we&#8217;re so proud of, knowing that it helps make [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/optinmonster-2018-recap-a-time-of-monster-growth/\">OptinMonster 2018 Recap: A Time of Monster Growth</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20196:\"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5uZXKpy9zMo?rel=0\" width=\"620\" height=\"348.75\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s hard to believe that another year has already gone by. <em>Cue Boyz II Men&#8217;s &#8220;It&#8217;s So Hard to Say Goodbye to Yesterday.&#8221;</em></p>\n<p>2018 was an awesome year for OptinMonster. Our customers are the reason we exist, so it&#8217;s an amazing feeling to deliver a product we&#8217;re so proud of, knowing that it helps make it possible for our customers to consistently reach and exceed their own goals.</p>\n<p>With the launch of our <strong>drag and drop campaign builder</strong>, it&#8217;s super simple to create beautiful campaigns without the need of a web developer or a designer.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129313\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drag-drop-update.gif\" alt=\"drag and drop builder functionality\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" /></p>\n<p>There&#8217;s so much you can do with the builder! From <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-a-landing-page/\">creating a simple landing page</a> to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-wordpress-menu-popup/\">opening an optin from a custom WordPress menu link</a>, we have tons of tutorials help you create OptinMonster campaigns that will grow your email list like mad.</p>\n<p>The last quarter of 2018 saw the opening of <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/university/\">OptinMonster University</a>, which brings courses, execution plans, and all of our ebooks, cheat sheets, templates, checklists, and other expert resources to YOU with the sole goal of exploding your business growth. The focus for all of the courses and execution plans is <strong>step-by-step, 100% actionable resources that you won&#8217;t find anywhere else</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5q7BUfXIy7I?rel=0\" width=\"620\" height=\"348.75\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>We also enthusiastically <strong>welcomed Thomas Griffin into his new role as OptinMonster&#8217;s President</strong> in September of 2018. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f60e.png\" alt=\"😎\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<h3>New Features Added in 2018</h3>\n<p>As if all that wasn&#8217;t enough, we introduced features and updates designed to make it <strong>easier than ever for you to get leads</strong>, increase conversions, and grow your business.</p>\n<p><strong>Gorgeous New Templates and Template Preview</strong></p>\n<p>We introduced several beautiful, professionally designed templates to make it super easy to create a stunning lead generation campaign in minutes.</p>\n<div class=\"envira-gallery-feed-output\"><img class=\"envira-gallery-feed-image\" tabindex=\"0\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/optinmonster-template-camber-390x215_c.png\" title=\"Camber\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p>We also added a preview feature so you can see exactly what each template will look like before you start building. This will make it easier to choose just the right template for your needs.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-124340\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/new-template-previews.gif\" alt=\"OptinMonster template previews\" width=\"800\" height=\"563\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Conversion Summary Report Emails</strong></p>\n<p>To help you stay on top of your campaign conversions, we created a weekly conversion email report:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-116375 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/conversion-summary-weekly-report.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster weekly conversion summary report\" width=\"620\" height=\"472\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/conversion-summary-weekly-report.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/conversion-summary-weekly-report-300x228.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>This includes your total conversions and best campaign performance for the week, plus more stats and links to our favorite resources that will help you <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/optinmonster-hacks-to-boost-your-conversions/\">boost your conversion rates</a>. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Improved Yes/No and Success Views</strong></p>\n<p>We beefed up our Yes/No and Success views to make your campaign options virtually limitless! You can control every view in your campaign &#8211; Yes/No, Optin, and Success &#8211; and can even redirect your leads to a URL instead of showing them a success view.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121121\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/button-success-actions.gif\" alt=\"optinmonster choose success actions for buttons\" width=\"800\" height=\"341\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-top-6-digital-increased-affiliate-revenue/\">Top 6 Digital</a> discovered that redirecting visitors to an affiliate offer with a strong call-to-action using an <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-activate-exit-intent-in-optinmonster/\">exit-intent optin</a> led to increased clicks on affiliate links. What awesome successes will you uncover?</p>\n<p><strong>Display Rule Upgrades</strong></p>\n<p>Display rules got a huge upgrade in 2018 and it&#8217;s easier than ever to decide exactly when and where your campaigns will appear.</p>\n<p>Both AND and OR conditions can be within a single ruleset and you also have the option to create entirely different rulesets.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121111\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/screenshot-display-rules-summary.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/screenshot-display-rules-summary.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/screenshot-display-rules-summary-300x178.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/screenshot-display-rules-summary-768x456.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>We also added even more ways to fine-tune campaigns and target your users based on the optins they&#8217;ve already seen and the URLs they&#8217;ve already visited. This makes it easy to take things even deeper by <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-use-monsterchains-to-display-your-campaigns-based-on-visitor-interaction/\">automating your funnel</a> with MonsterChains.</p>\n<p><strong>Timesaving Editing Tools</strong></p>\n<p>Customizing your campaign is even easier with the ability to import layouts and designs from another view in your campaign.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128382\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/import-layout-button-2.png\" alt=\"import layout button\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/import-layout-button-2.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/import-layout-button-2-300x158.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/import-layout-button-2-768x403.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also copy button styles and easily make customizations.</p>\n<p><strong>Powerful New Countdown Timer Actions</strong></p>\n<p>New countdown timer actions can maximize your results from a single campaign.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-125560\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"51\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann1-300x25.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For example, you could use a timer to count down to the beginning of your sale…</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-125561\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann2.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann2-300x24.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Then once the timer runs out, you can show a different view to count down to the end of your sale. This view could offer visitors another chance to sign up, this time for free shipping.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-125565\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann3c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"45\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann3c.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ann3c-300x22.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>After the event is over and your last timer has ended, you could show a simple success view asking visitors to sign up to be notified of the next sale. Just set the display rules to stop showing the campaign after whatever date you choose and you’re all set.</p>\n<p>That makes 3 opportunities for leads, sales, and engagement <strong>from a single OptinMonster campaign</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Minimized Slide-In Settings</strong></p>\n<p>New and improved slide settings can keep a slide-in optin around (just minimized) for your visitors and let them decide when they’re ready to engage. This can make an enormous difference in revenue and leads!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-125357\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/collapsed-slidein.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"512\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Access to Cutting Edge Features With OptinMonster&#8217;s Beta Program</strong></p>\n<p>You can opt in to our beta program from your <a href=\"https://app.optinmonster.com/account/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Account Settings</strong></a> by checking the box next to the <strong>Beta Program</strong> option.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-125544\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/beta-optin.png\" alt=\"opt in to beta program\" width=\"620\" height=\"239\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/beta-optin.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/beta-optin-300x116.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>This gives you exclusive, hands-on experience with brand new features before they’ve even been released!</p>\n<p><strong>Click-to-Call Abilities</strong></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve made adding a click-to-call button to your popup campaigns super easy. Your customers can reach you with the click or tap of a button, letting them know that you’re available and willing to answer their questions.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128379\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/add-click-to-call-button-2.gif\" alt=\"add click to call button to your campaign\" width=\"800\" height=\"429\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Improvements to Google Analytics Integration</strong></p>\n<p>In 2018, our Google Analytics integration got an update, making the 30-day snapshot that is displayed in your campaign dashboard (what you see when you log in) more accurate than ever. This means increased stability and more accurate reporting for you!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128509\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/updated-google-analytics-2.gif\" alt=\"updated google analytics integration\" width=\"800\" height=\"447\" /></p>\n<h3>Featured Case Studies</h3>\n<p>Our customers saw some absolutely incredibly successes in 2018. Here are just a few&#8230;</p>\n<p><strong>Woodside Communities</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-woodside-increased-revenue-294435-two-months/\">Woodside Communities</a> saw an opportunity to engage with visitors in a new way and executed quickly to get great results.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-119854\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/woodside_lightbox_planyourvisit.png\" alt=\"Woodside Communities helped prospects plan a visit using OptinMonster\" width=\"597\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/woodside_lightbox_planyourvisit.png 765w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/woodside_lightbox_planyourvisit-300x251.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Woodside Communities increased leads 476%.</li>\n<li>Woodside Communities increased revenue $294,435 in under two months.</li>\n<li>Woodside Communities went from 46 leads collected to 116 leads in just two months.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Expat.com</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-expat-com-grows-30000-members-month/\">Expat.com</a> works hard to personalize their visitor’s journey, and it nets them big results.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-119721\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/expat_exitintent.png\" alt=\"Expat.com adds over 14,000 members a month using OptinMonster exit intent\" width=\"800\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/expat_exitintent.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/expat_exitintent-300x146.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/expat_exitintent-768x372.png 768w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/expat_exitintent-620x300.png 620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Expat increased member registrations 50% using OptinMonster.</li>\n<li>Expat boosted registrations from 16,000/month to over 30,000/month.</li>\n<li>Expat refers 10% of a partner’s qualified leads using OptinMonster.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>SnackNation</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-snack-nation-adds-1200-segmented-leads/\">SnackNation</a> used OptinMonster to segment visitors, and lead them towards a sale.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-119365\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snacknation_lightbox_officeorhome-e1530285310243.png\" alt=\"SnackNation segments visitors using OptinMonster\" width=\"801\" height=\"518\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>SnackNation adds 1,200 new emails to their list each week using OptinMonster.</li>\n<li>SnackNation converts 15-20 qualified leads every day.</li>\n<li>SnackNation converts 31.85% of abandoning visitors.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Crossrope</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-crossrope-grew-list-900-percent-exit-intent-optins/\">Crossrope.com</a> invested heavily into their abandoning visitors and it paid off.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121776\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/crossrope_fullscreenchallenge.png\" alt=\"CrossRope drives challenge registrations with OptinMonster\" width=\"800\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/crossrope_fullscreenchallenge.png 800w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/crossrope_fullscreenchallenge-300x150.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/crossrope_fullscreenchallenge-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Crossrope.com converted 13.71% of abandoning visitors to active participants.</li>\n<li>Crossrope.com recovered 7.65% of abandoning shoppers.</li>\n<li>Crossrope.com increased subscribers by about 1800/month using OptinMonster.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>RocketBots</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-rocketbots-increased-list-680-onsite-retargeting/\">Rocketbots.io</a> uses OptinMonster to research their visitor’s interests and then creates more targeted campaigns in response.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-124321\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rocketbots_fullscreen_home-1024x638.png\" alt=\"Rocketbots targeted all visitors with full screen optins.\" width=\"800\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rocketbots_fullscreen_home-1024x638.png 1024w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rocketbots_fullscreen_home-300x187.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rocketbots_fullscreen_home-768x479.png 768w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rocketbots_fullscreen_home.png 1064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rocketbots converted 7.33% of targeted abandoning visitors.</li>\n<li>Rocketbots added 2.65% of sitewide visitors to their email list.</li>\n<li>Rocketbots saw a 680% increase in list growth.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We can&#8217;t wait to feature YOU in 2019!</p>\n<h3>Best of the OptinMonster Blog in 2018</h3>\n<p>The OptinMonster blog is full of all the best lead generation, SEO, email marketing, and content marketing tips, advice, best practices, and tutorials you need to make