trong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129210\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/mailchimp.png\" alt=\"mailchimp email marketing provider\" width=\"620\" height=\"201\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/mailchimp.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/mailchimp-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mailchimp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Mailchimp</a> always ranks high on any list of lead capture tools. That&#8217;s partly because it&#8217;s got an excellent free plan. If you&#8217;re sending fewer than 12,000 emails a month or your list is under 2000 subscribers, this is a great starting point. MailChimp also includes templates, guided newsletter creation, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/the-ultimate-guide-to-split-testing-your-email-newsletters/\">email subject line testing</a>, and a useful knowledge base.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Aweber</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129211\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber.png\" alt=\"aweber email marketing service\" width=\"620\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aweber.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Aweber</a> is an excellent email marketing tool for automated lead generation. It lets you easily create and send emails, and import content from your blog and share it with subscribers. It also has great analytics.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve chosen your email marketing tool, check out our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\">email marketing guide</a> to get started with email lead generation.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg3\">Email Address Finders</h3>\n<p>Sometimes you&#8217;re going to need to connect with people who aren&#8217;t on your email list. That means finding their email address and contact details. This next batch of tools will help with that.</p>\n<p><strong>5. Hunter</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129212\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter.png\" alt=\"hunter - best growth hacks\" width=\"620\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to do a quick email search, <a href=\"https://hunter.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hunter</a> is a useful tool. Just type in the domain, and it&#8217;ll find the email address pattern. Hunter also includes a confidence rating so you know if the email is likely to be right.</p>\n<p><strong>6. AeroLeads</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120213\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-aeroleads.png\" alt=\"aeroleads lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-aeroleads.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-aeroleads-300x167.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aeroleads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AeroLeads</a> provides a Google Chrome plugin to help you search LinkedIn, AngelList, and other networks for leads. Add those to your AeroLeads account, and this lead generation tool will find their business email addresses and other contact details. Then you&#8217;re ready to start reaching out.</p>\n<p><strong>7. Voila Norbert</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120214\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/7-norbert.png\" alt=\"use norbert for web based lead generation\" width=\"620\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/7-norbert.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/7-norbert-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.voilanorbert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Voila Norbert</a> promises to help you find and verify business email addresses. You can search in bulk for prospects with a CSV file. The tool also integrates with a wide range of CRM software. That makes it easy to keep track of your lead generation efforts.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg4\">Prospecting and Outreach Tools</h3>\n<p>Want to turn more of those contacts into leads and sales? These (mostly) automated lead generation tools will help with that process.</p>\n<p><strong>8. OutreachPlus</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129213\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/outreachplus.png\" alt=\"best growth hacks for outreach\" width=\"620\" height=\"289\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/outreachplus.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/outreachplus-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.outreachplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OutreachPlus</a> is one of several multi-purpose lead generation tools in this roundup. It lets you create and send personalized emails while still benefiting from automation. And it helps you find your best prospects for future outreach based on responses to your past or current campaigns.</p>\n<p><strong>9. Hoovers</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120215\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers.jpg\" alt=\"hoovers is online lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hoovers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hoovers</a> says it&#8217;s the world&#8217;s largest commercial database. You can use it to build targeted lists of new prospects. Hoovers includes company information to help you have more relevant conversations with those prospects. That helps you turn more prospects into leads and sales.</p>\n<p><strong>10. Datanyze</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120216\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze.png\" alt=\"top lead management software - datanyze\" width=\"620\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re in the business of technology, you can find leads based on data about the technology your target customers are already using. That&#8217;s what <a href=\"https://www.datanyze.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Datanyze</a> promises. It includes a prospecting tool to help you find contact details fast. Then you can export those to your CRM software for management and follow-up.</p>\n<p><strong>11. Lead Forensics</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129214\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics.png\" alt=\"lead generation marketing tools - lead forensics\" width=\"620\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics-300x144.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Sometimes you can miss out on good leads just because you don&#8217;t know everyone who visits your site. <a href=\"https://www.leadforensics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Lead Forensics</a> aims to solve that problem by getting contact details for anonymous website visitors. You can also score those prospects so you spend your time on those most likely to convert.</p>\n<p><strong>12. Growbots</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129215\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots.png\" alt=\"use growbots for automated lead generation\" width=\"620\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Know the market you want to target? <a href=\"https://www.growbots.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Growbots</a> will choose your best prospects from a database of more than 200 million contacts. You can easily get in touch with the right decision makers and follow up automatically. Growbots also includes testing so you can check which approaches are most effective.</p>\n<p><strong>13. Prospect.io</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120219\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio.png\" alt=\"prospectio is a web based lead generation tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://prospect.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Prospect.io</a> handles both prospecting and outreach. It helps you find and verify emails for your prospects. Then you can reach out to them via a range of templates. And you can easily track data on all interactions. Best of all, it integrates with a range of services to get contact information automatically.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg5\">CRM Tools</h3>\n<p>You can&#8217;t do a roundup of lead generation tools without including tools for customer relationship management (CRM). These tools help you connect and keep track of prospects and leads throughout the sales pipeline. Here are our picks.</p>\n<p><strong>14. Hubspot</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120220\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm.png\" alt=\"hubspot crm - lead generation tools\" width=\"552\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm-300x272.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\" /></p>\n<p>Hubspot has a suite of free tools, and <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hubspot CRM</a> is just one of them. But it&#8217;s a great way to organize, track and nurture leads. It tracks interactions automatically and helps you and your sales team keep on top of what&#8217;s happening.</p>\n<p><strong>15. Pardot</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129216\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot.png\" alt=\"pardot lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pardot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pardot</a> is a well-known lead generation tool that helps you manage and qualify leads. That ensures that you&#8217;re always talking to the best leads. Pardot includes fine-grained segmentation and automation for better communication with your future customers.</p>\n<p><strong>16. SharpSpring</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129217\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring.png\" alt=\"lead capture tools - sharpspring\" width=\"620\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring-300x137.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>In addition to its own built-in CRM, <a href=\"https://sharpspring.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">SharpSpring</a> integrates with all the top CRM lead management tools. That allows you to manage lead data across multiple platforms. SharpSpring includes custom deal stages and a useful pipeline overview, as well as other marketing tools.</p>\n<p><strong>17. Contactually</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120223\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually.jpg\" alt=\"contactually lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>It only takes a click to start managing your Google or Office365 contacts with <a href=\"https://www.contactually.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Contactually</a>. Once they&#8217;re connected, it&#8217;s easy to organize and segment contacts. You can also optimize workflow and schedule communication with Contactually&#8217;s AI tools.</p>\n<p><strong>18. Infusionsoft</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129218\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/infusionsoft.png\" alt=\"infusionsoft - lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/infusionsoft.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/infusionsoft-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.infusionsoft.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Infusionsoft</a> helps you keep customer information in one location. That lets you track interactions and responsiveness to guide future campaigns. It&#8217;s a multi-functional lead generation tool that&#8217;s definitely worth exploring.</p>\n<p><strong>19. Marketo</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129219\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/marketo.png\" alt=\"lead generation tools - marketo\" width=\"620\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/marketo.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/marketo-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The lead management solution from <a href=\"https://www.marketo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Marketo</a> helps businesses form relationships with prospective customers before they talk to sales reps. It helps you attract leads via inbound and outbound marketing, and improve the quality of the leads you get.</p>\n<p><strong>20. Nimble</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129220\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble.png\" alt=\"nimble lead gen tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble-300x207.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nimble.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nimble</a> pulls in information from a number of online sources, so you always have the latest data on potential leads. It makes it easy to identify and nurture key contacts without having to do any data entry. It&#8217;s available for major browsers, email programs, and mobile platforms.</p>\n<p><strong>21. OnePageCRM</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120231\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm.png\" alt=\"onepagecrm lead gen software\" width=\"620\" height=\"255\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm-300x123.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Looking for another simple piece of lead generation software? <a href=\"https://www.onepagecrm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OnePageCRM</a> grabs leads from Gmail, social media sites, and business networking sites to integrate them into your CRM. This software focuses on &#8220;next action sales,&#8221; so making sales is as simple as checking off your to-do list.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg6\">Sales Tools</h3>\n<p>For businesses, the goal of using lead generation tools is turning those leads into sales. And since the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-optimization-guide/#eco12\">best source of repeat business</a> is existing customers, it makes sense to use tools that both make sales and nurture your customers. Here are some tools to help with that.</p>\n<p><strong>22. Salesforce</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120227\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce.png\" alt=\"salesforce lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.salesforce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Salesforce</a> is among the world&#8217;s top sales and lead management software. It includes tools to help you manage leads, customers, sales teams and more. It integrates with a wide range of sales and marketing software to help businesses sell more and deliver better customer service.</p>\n<p><strong>23. Hubspot Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120228\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales.png\" alt=\"hubspot lead generation\" width=\"524\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales-300x286.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/sales\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hubspot Sales</a> is part of Hubspot&#8217;s suite of free tools for small businesses. It helps you save time on generating new leads. Hubspot Sales includes tools and templates for outreach and follow-up, so you can interact more efficiently with prospective customers.</p>\n<p><strong>24. LinkedIn Sales Navigator</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120229\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator.jpg\" alt=\"23 LinkedIn Sales Navigator\" width=\"620\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator-300x170.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Business networking site LinkedIn has huge amounts of company information in its databases. You can access that info via <a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/sales-solutions/sales-navigator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LinkedIn Sales Navigator</a>. This lead generation tool provides advanced lead searches and recommendations. It also includes CRM integrations and sales updates.</p>\n<p><strong>25. Pipedrive</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120242\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1.png\" alt=\"pipedrive lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pipedrive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pipedrive</a> prides itself on simplicity and it really is easy to use. This piece of automatic lead generation software tracks all interactions with leads easily. Then you can see all the data in one unified dashboard whenever you check in. It also makes it easy to know what action to take next.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg7\">Communication Tools</h3>\n<p>As we mentioned in our article on <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-checkout-page-optimization/#check8\">checkout page optimization</a>, talking to people who land on your site can help you win them as customers. That applies to leads, too. This next batch of lead generation tools will help with communication.</p>\n<p>First, let&#8217;s look at a few live chat tools.</p>\n<p><strong>26. Drift</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129221\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift.png\" alt=\"drift lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Drift</a> helps you deliver a helpful and personal service to customers by having a conversation with them. According to Drift, conversation drives half of all online sales, so this is crucial. This lead generation tool can help you wow your customers, and it includes a free level.</p>\n<p><strong>27. Intercom</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120244\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-intercom-1.png\" alt=\"intercom lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-intercom-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/27-intercom-1-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Need a modern messaging service to fully engage site visitors? <a href=\"https://www.intercom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Intercom</a> could be the answer. As well as being one of the best lead capture tools around, Intercom can help with customer support and onboarding.</p>\n<p><strong>28. Bontact</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120234\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact.jpg\" alt=\"bontact lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact-300x149.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Thinking of using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/facebook-messenger-marketing/\">Facebook Messenger</a> or WhatsApp Business to contact your leads? What about another platform? When you use <a href=\"https://bontact.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bontact</a>, you don&#8217;t have to choose. This lead generation app brings all your messaging under one roof to give you and your customers a unified, but cross-platform, experience.</p>\n<p><strong>29. Callpage</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129222\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage.png\" alt=\"lead gen tools - callpage\" width=\"620\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.callpage.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">CallPage</a> promises a 5-minute setup. After that, you can immediately start talking to visitors. Once they enter their phone number in the onscreen widget, they can be connected to you within seconds, no matter where they&#8217;re located. That lets you answer their question so you can win their business.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg8\">Advertising Tools</h3>\n<p>If you want to get leads by promoting your business you&#8217;ll need some lead generation tools to advertise your products and services. In addition to using social ads on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/products/ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/marketing-solutions/ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LinkedIn</a>, <a href=\"https://ads.twitter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a>, and others, here are some more lead generation services to try.</p>\n<p><strong>30. AdWords</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129223\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords.png\" alt=\"adwords content marketing\" width=\"620\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Google&#8217;s <a href=\"https://adwords.google.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AdWords</a> service puts ads in front of people when they search for related terms. That makes the ads relevant and increases the chances that searchers will visit your website or call your business. One great feature is that setting up campaigns is free. You only pay for advertising when people click your ad.</p>\n<p><strong>31. AdRoll</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129224\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll.png\" alt=\"adroll lead gen software\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.adroll.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AdRoll</a> helps display ads, social ads, and email work together to promote your business. It includes automation and rich insights so you can tweak campaigns for more growth.</p>\n<p><strong>32. AdEspresso</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129225\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso.png\" alt=\"adespresso lead gen\" width=\"620\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso-300x146.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Hootsuite&#8217;s <a href=\"https://adespresso.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AdEspresso</a> is an optimization tool for Facebook, Instagram, and Google ads. It lets you create and test multiple ad variants with only a few clicks. You can run ads with various audiences, too, and measure what&#8217;s most effective with in-depth analytics.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg9\">Other Lead Generation Tools</h3>\n<p>Finally, let&#8217;s complete our roundup with a few other lead generation tools.</p>\n<p><strong>33. Extole</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120238\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole.jpg\" alt=\"extole lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Word of mouth is a powerful lead generation tool. <a href=\"https://www.extole.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Extole</a> harnesses that by being an advocacy marketing platform. It helps you turn customers into advocates, who then help you generate more leads.</p>\n<p><strong>34. ReferralCandy</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120246\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1.png\" alt=\"referral candy lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.referralcandy.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ReferralCandy</a> helps eCommerce stores generate leads and sales by offering customers discounts for referring new business. You can easily customize a referral program for your business, and collect data on how the program is working.</p>\n<p><strong>35. WPForms</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-118698\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/9-wpf-surveys.gif\" alt=\"wpforms survey tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"464\" /></p>\n<p>One way to get more leads from website visitors is to find out what they want. You can use <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> to create a poll or survey that gets this important information. Or simply <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-freshsales-lead-form-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">integrate their simple drag and drop forms</a> with other lead capture tools.</p>\n<p><strong>36. Zapier</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120240\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier.png\" alt=\"zapier lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re wondering what Zapier&#8217;s doing on a list of lead generation tools, the answer&#8217;s simple. <a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Zapier</a>&#8216;s here because it allows you to connect multiple business services together, including some of the lead generation software in our roundup.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! We&#8217;ve covered a massive amount of information in this epic lead generation guide. Don&#8217;t forget to <a href=\"https://app.monstercampaigns.com/c/yzhozugk1mzrnd7mmmts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">download the free ebook</a> so you&#8217;ll always have easy access to this incredibly valuable info!</p>\n<p>For more excellent marketing tips and advice be sure to follow OptinMonster on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/optinmonster/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Optinmonster?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YouTube</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\">Lead Generation Strategies Proven to Boost Your Reach + FREE ebook</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1