se\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"social media\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=115286\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:566:\"<p>Shopify makes it super easy to get set up to sell online right out of the box. And, did you know that there are also hundreds of Shopify apps available to help you grow your business? But, with hundreds of Shopify apps out there, it can be hard to find the ones that will actually [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-shopify-apps-to-increase-sales-instantly/\">22 Best Shopify Apps to Increase Sales Instantly [Most Are FREE]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38145:\"<p>Shopify makes it super easy to get set up to sell online right out of the box. And, did you know that there are also hundreds of Shopify apps available to help you grow your business?</p>\n<p>But, with hundreds of Shopify apps out there, it can be hard to find the ones that will actually help you increase sales.</p>\n<p>We know that your revenue can&#8217;t grow without the right tools, so we&#8217;ve done a ton of research to find the <strong>best Shopify apps to increase sales</strong>.</p>\n<p>These apps will help you promote your store, sell your products, reward your customers, and handle inventory and shipping so you can earn more revenue. And, many of them are free! ⚡⚡⚡</p>\n<p>So, check it, our list of must-have apps for <a class=\"thirstylink\" title=\"Shopify\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Shopify store owners</a>. We&#8217;ve even broken it down into categories to make it easier to find what you need, with our top picks for each. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f381.png\" alt=\"🎁\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"#bestshopify1\">Marketing and Promotions</a><br />\n<a href=\"#bestshopify4\">Sales Channels</a><br />\n<a href=\"#bestshopify2\">Customer Service</a><br />\n<a href=\"#bestshopify3\">Products and Inventory</a><br />\n<a href=\"#bestshopify5\">Payment Plans</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"bestshopify1\">Marketing and Promotions</h3>\n<p>First, let&#8217;s start with the best Shopify apps to promote your store.</p>\n<p><strong>1. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OptinMonster</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127821\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-apps-optinmonster-2.png\" alt=\"best shopify apps optinmonster\" width=\"620\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-apps-optinmonster-2.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-apps-optinmonster-2-300x224.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve got no problem putting OptinMonster first on this list of the best Shopify apps to generate leads and increase sales. 🤩</p>\n<p>Of all the marketing apps on this list, OptinMonster&#8217;s ability to instantly lift sales easily makes it one of the top apps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cosmetic Capital <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-cosmetic-capital-increased-leads-by-300-using-a-floating-bar/\">increased leads by 300%</a> using a floating bar optin.</li>\n<li>White River <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-white-river-increased-mobile-conversions-150-percent/\">increased sales 35%</a> using OptinMonster&#8217;s responsive popups.</li>\n<li>The Eczema Company saw an <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-email-marketing-strategy-case-study-eczemacompany/\">instant 2.5X boost</a> in conversions after switching from another popup software.</li>\n<li>Scott Wyden Imagery is using OptinMonster to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-scott-wyden-imagery-reduced-woocommerce-cart-abandonment/\">recover 21% of abandoned shopping carts</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/category/case-studies/\">results speak for themselves</a>, but that&#8217;s not all that makes OptinMonster top our list. Our Shopify app also provides seamless integration of your OptinMonster account with Shopify, so you don&#8217;t need to install any special code. You can even use an OptinMonster popup to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-a-popup-coupon-that-boosts-sales/\">automatically apply discount codes to Shopify carts</a>!</p>\n<p>OptinMonster is the best option to gather email addresses, <a title=\"Shopify Conversion Optimization Guide\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/shopify-conversion-optimization/\">boost eCommerce conversions</a>, and make more sales. You can also target each optin to specific Shopify products, collections, pages, articles, and tags.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-123688\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify_display_rules-2.png\" alt=\"shopify display rules\" width=\"620\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify_display_rules-2.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify_display_rules-2-300x139.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>OptinMonster has all the advanced features you need to boost sales:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Showing targeted promotions (like free shipping banners, sales, and more) to visitors based on <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/referrer-detection/\">referral source</a>, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/geo-location-targeting/\">location</a>, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/onsite-follow-up-campaigns/\">onsite behavior</a>, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/device-based-targeting/\">device</a>, and more</li>\n<li>Using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\">Exit-Intent® Technology</a> or <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/inactivity-sensor-exit-intent-for-mobile/\">InactivitySensor</a>™ to reduce cart abandonment by gathering email addresses or showing an offer just before visitors leave your site</li>\n<li>Running retargeting campaigns to improve conversions with <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/onsite-retargeting/\">OnSite Retargeting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/integrations/\">Integrations</a> with your favorite email marketing, content management, and CRM platforms</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Here&#8217;s our guide to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/docs/how-to-integrate-optinmonster-with-shopify/\">integrating OptinMonster with Shopify</a> to help you get started.</p>\n<p>The OptinMonster Shopify app is $49 per month.</p>\n<p><strong>2. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/smile-io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Smile.io Rewards</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127852\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-smile.png\" alt=\"smile: rewards &amp; loyalty app for shopify\" width=\"620\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-smile.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-smile-300x223.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Whether customers stick to one brand or not, <a href=\"https://blog.accessdevelopment.com/2018-customer-loyalty-statistics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">loyalty programs</a> can be a huge draw. Customers enjoy engaging with brands, as well as the personalized service and rewards that come with these programs.</p>\n<p>With Smile.io you can offer a loyalty program on your Shopify store to create more loyal customers who boost your bank balance with repeat purchases.</p>\n<p>Smile.io lets you issue reward points based on creating accounts, sharing products on social media, following your brand, and more.</p>\n<p>These features are available for free, but you can upgrade to give additional rewards to your VIP customers and to enjoy full customization of your reward program. Upgrade pricing starts at $50 per month.</p>\n<p>Want to keep the interaction going after your customers open their accounts? Check out our guide to the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/7-types-of-emails-that-keep-customers-coming-back/\">7 types of emails that keep customers coming back</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>3. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/referralcandy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Referral Candy</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127846\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/referral-candy-shopifyapp.png\" alt=\"referral candy\" width=\"620\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/referral-candy-shopifyapp.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/referral-candy-shopifyapp-300x217.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Did you know that every happy customer <a href=\"https://www.groovehq.com/support/customer-support-statistics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">will tell nine more</a>? So, if you&#8217;re not finding a way to get referrals, you&#8217;re missing out on sales.</p>\n<p>Referral Candy is one of the best Shopify apps to give your customers incentives to refer their friends. You can choose the reward of your choice for unlimited referrals.</p>\n<p>The Referral Candy system includes automatic reward delivery and referral reminders, as well as a dashboard where you can track referrals. This app starts at $49 per month.</p>\n<p>Want to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/psychograpic-marketing-generates-leads/\">learn more about your customers&#8217; secret thoughts</a> so you can drive even more sales? Here&#8217;s how you can create a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-a-wordpress-survey-popup/\">WordPress survey popup</a> with OptinMonster.</p>\n<p><strong>4. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/plug-in-seo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Plug in SEO</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-127844 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/plug-in-seo-app.png\" alt=\"plug-in seo google shopping optimization\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/plug-in-seo-app.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/plug-in-seo-app-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Plug in SEO is our pick for one of the best free Shopify apps because it helps you find, troubleshoot, and fix <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ultimate-seo-guide/\">search engine optimization (SEO)</a> issues so you can get more web traffic to your online store.</p>\n<p>This free app automatically checks for issues with page titles and descriptions, structure, speed, and more. It includes code snippets you can use to fix any issues yourself.</p>\n<p>If you need additional features, like bulk editing, structured data support, and multilingual SEO, you&#8217;ll need to upgrade to the pro version of the app, which is $20 per month.</p>\n<p>Learn more tips to rank higher in search results in our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/shopify-seo-guide/\">Shopify SEO</a> guide. Or, breathe life into your outdated SEO with these new <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/updating-outdated-seo/\">SEO best practices</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>5. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/social-photos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Social Photos</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-127849 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-socialphotos.png\" alt=\"socialphotos shopify app lets you sell products with direct links\" width=\"620\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-socialphotos.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-socialphotos-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Want to drive more Shopify sales from <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-generate-leads-on-instagram/\">Instagram</a>? Social Photos could be the app you&#8217;ve been looking for. This app helps you feature your customers (making them happy) and get an awesome kind of <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/11-ways-to-use-social-proof-to-increase-your-conversions/\">social proof</a> called <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/user-generated-content/\">user-generated content</a> at the same time.</p>\n<p>When customers tag photos of themselves using your products on Instagram, Social Photos automatically collates them into a gallery. Every photo can then be used to sell products through direct links, driving more sales.</p>\n<p>You can highlight the best customer photos to encourage new customers to buy, and can also create themed products images galleries. Social Photos also lets you interact with Instagram photos from the page where the photos appear.</p>\n<p>You can find Social Photos in the Shopify app store starting at $10 per month for the basic package, and it goes up to $50 per month for the full range of features.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bestshopify4\">Sales Channels</h3>\n<p><strong>6. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/facebook-store\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook Channel</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127848\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-facebook-channel.png\" alt=\"facebook channel shopify apps\" width=\"620\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-facebook-channel.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-apps-facebook-channel-300x189.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>While <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/email-marketing-vs-social-media-performance-2016-2019-statistics/\">email marketing is more effective than social media</a> at driving sales, social media is still an important referral source for online stores. In fact, both Facebook and Twitter can help you gain product recommendations, and actual sales.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128982\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/facebook-channel-screenshot.png\" alt=\"facebook sales channel desktop view\" width=\"620\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/facebook-channel-screenshot.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/facebook-channel-screenshot-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why Facebook Channel makes our list of the best Shopify apps to increase sales. It lets you use your Facebook presence to drive sales, setting a Facebook store up in just a few clicks. With Facebook Channel, you can highlight products on your Facebook timeline and let shoppers purchase products directly from your posts.</p>\n<p>Facebook Channel is a free app. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>Check out our guide to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-get-traffic-from-facebook-for-free/\">getting traffic from Facebook</a> to get even more sales from your Shopify store. You can also <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-a-like-us-on-facebook-popup-with-optinmonster/\">create a custom &#8220;Like Us On Facebook&#8221; popup</a> to drive traffic from your website to your Facebook business page!</p>\n<p><strong>7. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/messenger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Messenger Channel</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128985\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-2.png\" alt=\"messenger shopify app\" width=\"620\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-2.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-2-300x154.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>With the growth of messaging apps and smart speakers, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/conversational-commerce/\">conversational commerce</a> continues to grow at a rapid pace. Take advantage of this trend with the Messenger sales channel app for Shopify.</p>\n<p>With this free app connected to Shopify, you can add a &#8220;message us&#8221; button to your online store, making it easy to have real-time conversations with your customers. But it doesn&#8217;t end with real-time communications.</p>\n<p>Shoppers can also browse products and make purchases from your Messenger chat and you can send automated order updates.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128986\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-screenshot.png\" alt=\"messenger mobile sales example\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-screenshot.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/messenger-channel-screenshot-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll be able to fulfill Messenger orders from Shopify and track Facebook sales in your sales channel overview and Analytics pages.</p>\n<p><strong>8. <a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/buy-button\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Buy Button Channel</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128988\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-channel.png\" alt=\"buy button channel\" width=\"620\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-channel.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-channel-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The free Buy Button sales channel app is simple but effective. You can use it to create a customized buy button that you can put anywhere to let shoppers purchase with a click. No muss, no fuss.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128989\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-screenshot.png\" alt=\"but button sales channel screenshot\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-screenshot.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/buy-button-screenshot-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can change the button colors to match your brand, create custom checkout links for any product, and update product details from Shopify without needing to edit any code on your site or blog.</p>\n<p>With the Buy Button, you can fulfill orders made with both the buttons and just the custom checkout links. And, you can track sales using your Home sales overview and Analytics pages.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bestshopify2\">Best Shopify Apps for Customer Service</h3>\n<p>Next, let&#8217;s look at the top apps for customer service.</p>\n<p><strong>9. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/facebook-messenger-live-chat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook Live Chat</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127850\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-facebook-live-chat.png\" alt=\"facebook live chat\" width=\"620\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-facebook-live-chat.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-facebook-live-chat-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Live chat has become an important customer service and <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-ways-to-collect-customer-feedback/\">customer feedback</a> tool. According to recent <a href=\"https://www.kayako.com/live-chat-software/statistics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">surveys</a>, businesses say offering live chat has had a positive effect on sales, revenue, and customer loyalty. And with more than 2 billion users, Facebook is one of the best social media sites to connect with your customers.</p>\n<p>The Facebook Live Chat Shopify app lets you support your customers on your Shopify site by using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/facebook-messenger-marketing/\">Facebook Messenger</a> for customer service. The app also integrates with other social sites and features a user-friendly, responsive design.</p>\n<p>This app is free for up to three websites, with upgrade packages ranging from $9.99 to $49.99 per month.</p>\n<p><strong>10. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/one-click-social-login\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">One Click Social Login</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127841\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-one-click-social-login.png\" alt=\"one click social login makes customer onboarding easy\" width=\"620\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-one-click-social-login.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-one-click-social-login-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The easier you make it for customers to create accounts, the sooner you can offer them the right products and make sales.</p>\n<p>One Click Social Login lets your customers create accounts on your Shopify store by logging in with their existing social media credentials. Accounts supported include Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Pinterest, Amazon, and many more.</p>\n<p>There&#8217;s also an easy admin panel so you can easily configure the simple settings.</p>\n<p>One Click Social Login starts at $4.99 per month, but you can upgrade to see your customers&#8217; social profiles and make additional customizations.</p>\n<p><strong>11. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/yotpo-social-reviews\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Yotpo</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127843\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-yotpo.png\" alt=\"yotpo shopify app\" width=\"620\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-yotpo.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-shopify-yotpo-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Yotpo consistently ranks among the best apps to increase sales because it helps you get more product reviews to drive purchases from social proof.</p>\n<p>This app lets you easily send out requests for customer reviews and showcase reviews in widgets and store tabs. You can moderate all reviews received, and can also use Yotpo to get social media traffic to your store.</p>\n<p>Yotpo is free, but if you want additional features such as user-generated photos, rich snippets, and more, pricing starts at $29 per month.</p>\n<p><strong>12. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/swell\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Rewards and Referrals by Swell</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127847\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/rewards-referrals-app.png\" alt=\"rewards and referrals by swell ARE swell\" width=\"620\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/rewards-referrals-app.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/rewards-referrals-app-300x179.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>One of the reasons we&#8217;ve included Swell, even though there are both rewards and referrals apps already on the list, is because it has so many integrations. As well as working with Yotpo, which we mentioned above, it works with Facebook, Hubspot, Mailchimp, and more.</p>\n<p>Swell says its users have doubled business from existing customers, thanks to rewards for writing reviews, referring new customers, creating accounts, making new purchases, and more. You can also reward social media interactions such as likes and follows.</p>\n<p>Swell is free for up to 100 orders each month. After that, plans start at $29 per month.</p>\n<p><strong>13. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/swym-relay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Wishlist Plus</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127854\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wishlist-plus-shopify.png\" alt=\"wishlist plus app\" width=\"620\" height=\"257\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wishlist-plus-shopify.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wishlist-plus-shopify-300x124.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.com/ian-mills/4-ways-wishlists-can-boost-your-website-sales_b_9417882.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Wishlists</a> are a great way to learn more about what your customers want, so you can connect with them to make more sales. Wishlist Plus lets you collect information about customer preferences, and they don&#8217;t even have to be logged in. 🤯</p>\n<p>This app integrates with your Shopify store and lets you keep track of items and engagement within a dashboard. For customers, Wishlist Plus is a hassle-free way to store their desired purchases and even share those with others.</p>\n<p>Wishlist Plus is free for up to 100 items, then plans range from $9.99 to $29.99 per month.</p>\n<p>Want to get even more from your online store? Check out our guide to how to write a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-write-a-sales-page-that-converts/\">sales page that converts</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bestshopify3\">Best Shopify Apps for Products and Inventory</h3>\n<p>This category includes apps to help you manage your product catalog, plus the periods before and after shipping.</p>\n<p><strong>14. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/printful\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Printful</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-127845 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/printful-best-shopify-apps.png\" alt=\"printful makes it super easy to sell online\" width=\"620\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/printful-best-shopify-apps.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/printful-best-shopify-apps-300x191.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want a Shopify store without the need to warehouse your own products Printful can help. This app provides print-on-demand designs for T-shirts, bags, mugs, and almost anything else that can be printed. They&#8217;ve even got designers who&#8217;ll help you create the most appealing products.</p>\n<p>Once they&#8217;re ready, just take orders from your store and Printful will send them out. No need to manage inventory or print shipping labels. It&#8217;s a great way to make sales with no hassle. <a href=\"https://www.printful.com/custom-products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Cost varies</a> depending on the product to sell.</p>\n<p><strong>15. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/oberlo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Oberlo</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-127842 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-apps-oberlo.png\" alt=\"oberlo shopify app makes it easy to sell online\" width=\"620\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-apps-oberlo.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/best-apps-oberlo-300x191.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Oberlo offers a similar service to Printful by letting you add products to your store and dropshipping them straight to your customers.</p>\n<p>But with this app, you&#8217;re not limited to items that can be printed. You can choose products from AliExpress and the Oberlo Marketplace and add them to your store with a couple of clicks.</p>\n<p>Oberlo offers automatic order fulfillment and inventory management. You can also customize products, connect Oberlo with your existing products, and even allow other people to help run your store.</p>\n<p>Oberlo is free for 500 products and up to 50 orders per month. For additional products, orders and features, you can upgrade at between $29.90 and $79.90 per month.</p>\n<p>To get more from using Oberlo products, check out our tips on how to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-email-marketing-tips/\">skyrocket your eCommerce sales</a> with email marketing.</p>\n<p><strong>16. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/returns-center-by-aftership\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AfterShip Returns Center</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127839\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-aftership.png\" alt=\"aftership returns center app\" width=\"612\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-aftership.png 612w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-aftership-300x245.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" /></p>\n<p>Sometimes your customers will want to return a product, but it can be a pain to manage the process. AfterShip makes managing product returns easy.</p>\n<p>It gives you a branded returns center that lets customers submit returns in a couple of clicks. Later, it&#8217;ll automatically inform them of the status of their returns and any refunds.</p>\n<p>This is one of the best Shopify apps around, and it&#8217;s free for 5 returns per month. Paid plans start at $9 per month.</p>\n<p><strong>17. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/zine-builder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Catalog Maker</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127853\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wholesale-catalog.png\" alt=\"wholesale catalog maker\" width=\"620\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wholesale-catalog.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/wholesale-catalog-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>A product catalog is a great way to show off your products images and boost sales, but how do you create one? If you&#8217;re not a great designer but have a lot of products, you need a tool that makes the process easy. Catalog Maker could be that tool.</p>\n<p>It lets you quickly create professional looking catalogs from your Shopify collections, and you can use drag and drop editing to create a catalog with one of the app&#8217;s templates.</p>\n<p>In addition to catalogs, you can create invoices, receipts, product recommendations, and even thank you notes. Pricing starts at $25.</p>\n<p><strong>18. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/pre-order\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pre-Order Manager</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127851\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-pre-order-manager.png\" alt=\"pre-order manager app lets you take advantage of advance sales\" width=\"620\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-pre-order-manager.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shopify-pre-order-manager-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>When you generate buzz with your seasonal or <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/holiday-email-marketing-tips-examples/\">holiday email marketing</a>, it&#8217;s useful to let people pre-order items from your store. And pre-orders are a great way to figure out which products are most likely to be successful.</p>\n<p>Pre-Order Manager lets you take advance orders from visitors to your store with a pre-order button for out of stock items. You can edit button text, change the setting by location, and even turn pre-orders on and off storewide. You can also limit the number of available pre-orders for any product.</p>\n<p>Pricing for Pre-Order Manager starts at $24.95 per month after a 14-day free trial.</p>\n<p><strong>19. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/back-in-stock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Back in Stock</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-127840\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-back-in-stock.png\" alt=\"back in stock app\" width=\"620\" height=\"505\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-back-in-stock.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/apps-back-in-stock-300x244.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Sold out of your best products? With Back in Stock, you don&#8217;t need to lose sales. Our last app in the list of best Shopify apps lets your customers sign up to be notified when a product they want is back in your store. Once it is, they get an automatic email notification.</p>\n<p>This easy to install app also helps you understand which products are most popular so you can manage stock levels. You can also customize any aspect of the app to meet your needs.</p>\n<p>Back in Stock starts at $19 per month, with plans up to $79 per month.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bestshopify5\">Payment Plans</h3>\n<p>Our last category includes Shopify apps that help you get set up to accept recurring and partial payments. This means that you can let shoppers spread out payments on high-ticket items or set up recurring payments for subscription services.</p>\n<p><strong>20. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/partial-ly-payment-plans\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Partial.ly Payment Plans</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128991\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/partially-shopify-app.png\" alt=\"partial.ly payment plans\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/partially-shopify-app.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/partially-shopify-app-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Partial.ly gives shoppers the option to complete their purchase using standard checkout or with Partial.ly payment plans. If they opt for Partial.ly, once they enter their payment details, the order automatically gets added to your Shopify admin and all future payments are timed and automated.</p>\n<p>As the store owner, you have full control over the fee, down payment, term, and payment frequency. You can also allow shoppers to set up automated or manual payment plans.</p>\n<p>Partial.ly integrates with Stripe, so you&#8217;re covered to accept all major credit cards plus a lot more, and it&#8217;s free to install. They charge 5% + $0.30 per transaction.</p>\n<p><strong>21. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/paywhirl-recurring-payments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">PayWhirl Recurring Payments</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128992\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-orders-app.png\" alt=\"recurring payments &amp; orders shopify app examples\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-orders-app.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-orders-app-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>With PayWhirl Recurring Payments your customers will be able to manage their own account details, update their payment and credit card information, add or remove payment plans, and purchase subscriptions on their own, saving time for you and <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/user-onboarding-best-practices-to-easily-boost-customer-success/\">reducing friction for your customers</a>.</p>\n<p>For subscription services, PayWhirl has a &#8220;Build a Box&#8221; feature that offers shoppers customizable subscription packages, which is a super cool feature. Subscription boxes are HUGE right now, and allowing shoppers to customize their subscription box could be used as an upsell. FabFitFun does this successfully with their subscription boxes.</p>\n<p>PayWhirl Recurring Payments has a ton of other features like a failed payments management system, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/upselling-tips-and-examples/\">upsell funnels</a>, trial periods, and more. The Shopify app does have a free-to-install version for Stripe; other plans include all payment gateways and start at $49/month and have a 14-day free trial. Successful transaction rates start at 3% and go down to 0.5% as monthly plan costs increase.</p>\n<p><strong>22. <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/recurring-invoices\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Recurring Payments</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128993\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-app.png\" alt=\"recurring payments shopify credit card app\" width=\"620\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-app.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/recurring-payments-app-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Recurring Payments allows shoppers to buy subscriptions, purchase using payment plans, or pay invoices without login or registration. For subscription customers without an account who want to cancel, they can do so easily by clicking the unsubscribe link in their subscription confirmation email.</p>\n<p>Instead of automatically billing customers, this app allows eCommerce business owners to automatically generate invoices that customers can then pay using whatever method they choose at the time; there&#8217;s no need for customers to remember to make changes or updates to their payment methods in their account.</p>\n<p>Recurring Payments is $15.95/month with a 14-day free trial.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Now that you know the best Shopify apps to increase sales, why not get even more sales from your store with a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-run-a-successful-email-marketing-campaign/\">successful email marketing campaign</a>? You can also improve store promotion with these <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/promotional-email-examples-and-how-to-write-your-own/\">promotional email examples</a>. And, check out our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/shopify-abandoned-cart-recovery/\">tips on Shopify abandoned cart recovery</a> to boost your revenue.</p>\n<p>Don&#8217;t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YouTube</a> for more helpful guides, tutorials, and resource lists.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-shopify-apps-to-increase-sales-instantly/\">22 Best Shopify Apps to Increase Sales Instantly [Most Are FREE]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-shopify-apps-to-increase-sales-instantly/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:30:\"https://optinmonster.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:11:{s:6:\"server\";s:12:\"n